{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast, LLM-based agents excel at rapidly processing large datasets, performing repetitive tasks with high accuracy, and detecting patterns that might elude human observers.",
    "Current State.",
    "Several LMA systems incorporate human-in-the-loop designs.",
    "For instance, AISD [162] involves human input during requirement analysis and system validation, where users provide feedback on use cases, system designs, and prototypes.",
    "Similarly, MARE [59] leverages human assessment to refine generated requirements and specifications."
  ]
}